Class
Description
Constant
Constant Enum Class holds all variables with constant values Stores the value corresponding to each constant
Date
Date Class is a blueprint for date objects Stores the month, day, and year of date
FitnessClass
FitnessClass stores member databases for classes offered to members Includes methods to check in and drop classes
FitnessOptions
Enum class that contains all fitness classes, including information about time, instructor, and course name
GymManager
User Interface class that processes commands entered into the console Focuses on commands relating to gym member management, such as Add Member, Remove Member, Check In Member
Location
Location Enum Class holds constant Locations, expressed by zipcode and county of gym Stores the following data: - zipCode - county
Member
Member Class is a blueprint for member objects Stores the following member data: - First and Last name - Date of Birth - Date of Membership Expiration - Location of Gym Membership
MemberDatabase
MemberDatabase is a class to store and sort gym members Stores the following data: - Member list - Size of list
Month
Month Enum Class holds all months Stores the following data: - Month's expression as a number - Last day in month (28 for February)
RunProject1
Driver class to run Project 1
SortCategory
SortCategory Enum Class holds all potential categories of sorting members
Time
Time Enum Class holds constant times when gym classes can occur Stores the following time data: - hour - minute
